FBIS3-33055 "drlat033_r_94004" FBIS-LAT-94-033 Document Type:Daily Report 17 Feb 1994 Peru Foreign Minister Efrain Goldenberg To Replace Bustamante PA1702050194 Hamburg DPA in Spanish 0444 GMT 17 Feb 94 PA1702050194 Hamburg DPA Language: Spanish Article Type:BFN [Text] Lima, 16 Feb (DPA) -- Foreign Minister Efrain Goldenberg was designated new prime minister [as received] of Peru tonight, replacing Alfonso Bustamante, who resigned due to his differences about how the thorny "La Cantuta case" was handled, it has been officially announced.
